#

Simple Creamy Cauliflower Soup

40 min
$10
220 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

Dairy

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-Free

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Soup

Tags:

SoupComfort FoodEasy

Description

A velvety smooth soup that warms the soul, perfect for a cozy night in.

Ingredients

  • cauliflower: 1 large head, chopped
  • onion: 1, chopped
  • garlic: 2 cloves, minced
  • vegetable broth: 4 cups
  • heavy cream: 1 cup
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
